OL,7,FA man who served years behind bars
OL,8,Fbefore his conviction was overturned
OL,9,Fhas lost a challenge at the European
OL,10,FCourt of Human Rights over his
OL,11,Frejected compensation claims.
OL,13,FSam Hallam, who was convicted of
OL,14,Fmurder, previously brought legal
OL,15,Faction at the High Court over the
OL,16,FJustice Secretary's refusal to award
OL,17,Fthem payouts.
