OL,5,Ccompensation bid
OL,7,FBut in a judgment on Tuesday, a panel
OL,8,Fof judges at the ECHR ruled with a
OL,9,Fmajority of 12 to 5 that there had
OL,10,Fbeen no violation of Mr Hallam's
OL,11,Frights.
OL,13,FHis lawyer argued he had suffered a
OL,14,Fbreach of part of Article 6 of the
OL,15,FEuropean Convention on Human Rights,
OL,16,Fwhich says everyone charged with a
OL,17,Fcriminal offence should be presumed
OL,18,Finnocent until proven guilty.
