OL,7,FHowever, lawyers for the UK government
OL,8,Fsaid the decision-maker "was required
OL,9,Fto decide on compensation in
OL,10,Faccordance with criteria which focused
OL,11,Fonly on the specific effect of a new
OL,12,For newly discovered fact, rather than
OL,13,Fmaking a general assessment of guilt
OL,14,For innocence".
