OL,7,F"To find in the negative that it could
OL,8,Fnot be shown to the very high standard
OL,9,Fof proof of beyond reasonable doubt
OL,10,Fthat an applicant did not commit an
OL,11,Foffence ` by reference to a new or
OL,12,Fnewly discovered fact or otherwise `
OL,13,Fis not tantamount to a positive
OL,14,Ffinding that he or she did commit the
OL,15,Foffence."
