OL,5,Ccompensation bid
OL,7,FMr Hallam, from east London, served
OL,8,Fmore than seven years after he was
OL,9,Fsentenced to life as a teenager
OL,10,Ffollowing his conviction at the Old
OL,11,FBailey in 2005 for the murder of a
OL,12,Ftrainee chef.
OL,14,FHe was freed after appeal judges ruled
OL,15,Ffresh evidence made his conviction
OL,16,Funsafe.
OL,18,FMr Hallam's conviction was quashed in
OL,19,F2012.
